snippet.title: Timespinner - Launch Trailer (PC, PS4 & PS Vita)
snippet.description:
Available on September 25th 2018, on PC, Mac, Linux, PS4 & PS Vita. 
Wishlist now to be alerted when it arrives! : https://store.steampowered.com/app/368620/Timespinner/

Travel back in time to change fate itself, in this beautifully crafted story-driven adventure, inspired by classic 90s action-platformers. Join timekeeper Lunais on her quest for revenge against the empire that killed her family, using time-bending powers to explore a vast, connected world.

For more information and to keep up to date with the latest development news, visit the Timespinner website: http://timespinnergame.com/

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/timespinner
Website: http://timespinnergame.com/
Lunar Ray Games on Twitter: https://twitter.com/lunarraygames
Chucklefish on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ChucklefishLTD

Developed by Lunar Ray Games, published by Chucklefish.
